room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
review: Very well put together room!  Enjoyed it quite a bit, the puzzles were well thought out

room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
review: I'm still pondering the ingenious design/engineering that went into the Mad Hatter room. An incredible, engaging experience! We loved every minute and the staff are the best!

room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
review: A college friend and I took our daughters to The Great Escape of La Crosse last week. With girls ranging in age from 7-16, we were mere seconds from escaping the Mad Hatter room. It was challenging, intriguing, captivating, and fantastic!

room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
review: It was a lot of fun! We went through the Mad Hatter room. The puzzles were challenging. The theming was fun and you can tell the owner really enjoys putting these rooms together.
